{"tid":1287386,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[7.7] 黃絲藍絲不和解不是夢？","createTime":"2019-07-05T07:45:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T07:47:00.000Z","uid":12179,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3ce27abab5acce8400000a50e8745867ee223f0f","tid":1287386,"uid":12179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:45:44.000Z","msg":"對黃絲黎講，自由、人權、民主、法治、公民社會，係佢地一直追求，放首位既事。<br />\n<br />\n對藍絲(唔計個d盲撐，唔講道理)黎講，社會繁榮，穩定，安居樂業係佢地放首位既事。<br />\n<br />\n唔通追求一樣野代表另一樣唔重要？唔係，只係相對次要。問題係香港要追求自由、人權、民主、法治、公民社會既同時會損害到社會穩定。正常追求一樣唔應該損害到另一樣。<br />\n<br />\n咁點解會咁？係咪因為政府？<br />\n<br />\n勿分化、勿捉鬼、不篤灰、不抹黑、不割蓆，係咪只要係香港人都應該咁？係咪政府先搞到今日有分黃絲藍絲？<br />\n<br />\n7.7 希望黃絲藍絲大和解，700萬人一齊出黎令政府回應我地訴求，之後香港回復繁榮穩定。咁樣香港先可以贏，香港人團結先可以贏。<br />\n<br />\n大家都得到想要既野，何樂而不為？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WqbZwv7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWqbZwv7.png&h=4bdb7177&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ti6R64s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fti6R64s.png&h=bdaf52fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vFrOpQ8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvFrOpQ8.png&h=6f6f6064&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zVQSRv8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzVQSRv8.png&h=97e63410&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n得返兩日！大家將注意力放返係7.7遊行！"},{"pid":"ce21f046d7f3250a25b272e020995154d54776e7","tid":1287386,"uid":12179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:46:14.000Z","msg":"大和解先岩，打錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"319ed890d690a326b79b84a91441bc4aea1d364e","tid":1287386,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:46:44.000Z","msg":"五毛可以用武漢分化我地，我地都可以利用武漢將把火燒上大陸，但記住唔係幫武漢，77當日要集中係五大訴求先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfWtfJ.jpg\" dat